    "The process was both quick and inexpensive owing to the small size of the LLM and the fact that the fine-tuning was conducted in the cloud, via the OpenAI's API.",
    "Two Case StudiesIn this section, we present two examples to demonstrate the capabilities of ChronoLLM-one is a simple double arm system (or double pendulum), the other one is a truck.",
    "Each example is accompanied by an input prompt, the corresponding generated PyChrono scripts, and frames that we obtained upon executing the PyChrono scripts, i.e., running the simulations.",
    "Note that these types of models might be considered \"in-distribution\" for ChronoLLM, as they are generated using data that was qualitatively similar to the one used to train ChronoLLM.",
    "We argue that this is not a significant issue."
